{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2018}}
The '''Robert Award for Best Actor in a Leading Television Role''' ({{lang-da|Robert Prisen for årets mandlige hovedrolle – tv-serie}}) is one of the merit awards presented by the [[Danish Film Academy]] at the annual [[Robert Awards]] ceremony. The award has been handed out since 2013.

== Honorees ==

=== 2010s ===
* 2013: [[Nikolaj Lie Kaas]] – ''[[The Killing (Danish TV series)|Forbrydelsen 3]]''
* 2014: [[Kim Bodnia]] – ''[[The Bridge (Danish/Swedish TV series)|Broen II]]''
* 2015: [[Carsten Bjørnlund]] – ''[[The Legacy (TV series)|The Legacy]]''<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvtid.tv2.dk/2015-02-01-se-listen-her-er-alle-robert-vinderne |title=Se listen: Her er alle Robert-vinderne |work=Tvtid.tv2.dk |accessdate=8 March 2015}}</ref>
