{{Infobox company | name = Stillking Films | logo = | logo_caption = | image = | image_caption = | type = [[Privately held company|Private]] | industry = Motion picture, television, music | foundation = Prague, Czech Republic ({{Start date and age|1993}}) | founder = Matthew Stillman | location_city = [[Prague]] | location_country = Czech Republic | locations = 8 | area_served = | key_people = Matthew Stillman, Daniel Bergmann<ref>{{cite web|last1=Media|first1=News|title=Stillking Films s Partizanem získaly Samsung|url=http://www.mediar.cz/stillking-films-s-partizanem-ziskaly-samsung/|accessdate=5 August 2016}}</ref> | products = [[Casino Royale (2006 film)|Casino Royale]], [[Snowpiercer]], [[Legends (TV series)|Legends]] | assets = | equity = | owner = | num_employees = | parent = | divisions = | subsid = Stillking Cape Town Radio House, Motel Productions, Stillking London, Stillking Santiago De Chile, Stillking USA, Pioneer Stillking Films | homepage = http://www.stillking.com/ | footnotes = | intl = | bodystyle = }} '''Stillking Films''' is a production company based in the Czech Republic. Its films include ''[[Mission Impossible Ghost Protocol]]'', ''[[Child 44]]'', ''[[Snowpiercer]]'' and others. It is owned by Matthew Stillman.<ref name="borovannejvice">{{cite web|title=Nejvíce veřejných peněz proteklo přes filmovou produkci Stillking Films |url= http://www.borovan.cz/17531/nejvice-verejnych-penez-proteklo-pres-filmovou-produkci-stillking-films |accessdate= 5 August 2016 |language=cs-CZ |date=13 November 2014}}</ref>
Stillking Films is the biggest production company in the Czech Republic.<ref>{{cite web|title=Stillking Films přiváží do ČR nejvíc nových produkcí|url=http://strategie.e15.cz/zpravy/stillking-films-privazi-do-cr-nejvic-novych-produkci-418092|accessdate=5 August 2016|date=16 March 2010}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Přes Stillking Films protekly filmové a TV dotace v objemu téměř 400 milionů|url=http://www.borovan.cz/24836/pres-stillking-films-protekly-filmove-a-tv-dotace-pres-350-milionu|website=Borovan.cz|accessdate=6 August 2016|language=cs-CZ|date=13 January 2016}}</ref>
==History== Stillking was founded by Matthew Stillman in 1993. Its purpose was to bring production of big films in the Czech Republic. The company co-produced its first full-length film in 1995. Other followed in next years. Company has grown and established its subsidiaries in United Kingdom, South Africa, Spain and Chile.<ref>{{cite web |title= Chceme jen to, co je běžné všude - rozhovor s producentem Matthewem Stillmanem|url=http://www.culturenet.cz/aktuality/chceme-jen-to-co-je-bezne-vsude-rozhovor-s-producentem-matthewem-stillmanem/n:3084/ |website= www.culturenet.cz |accessdate= 5 August 2016}}</ref>
==Offices== * Stillking Films [[Barrandov Film Studios]] - Prague * Stillking Cape Town Radio House - Cape Town * Motel Productions - Barcelona * Stillking London - London * Stillking Santiago De Chile - Santiago De Chile * Stillking USA - Los Angeles * Pioneer Stillking Films - Budapest * Icon Films - Bucharest
